  "title": "Assistant Superintendent | Welfare Home",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee operation of a welfare home ensuring the well-being of residents and compliance with SOP and law regulation</li>\n  <li>Ensure attention and support meet with the Destitute Person Act and MSF regulation</li>\n  <li>Maintain safety and cleanliness with compliance standards</li>\n  <li>Ensure Food Safety and Hygiene are strictly adhere</li>\n  <li>Evaluate and enhance the quality and relevance of home programs and services</li>\n  <li>Preparation of budgets and monitor cash flow according to policies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma/ Degree in social work.</li>\n  <li>2 years of relevant working experience in the social service sector.</li>\n  <li>Ability to commit to weekend and evening meetings when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Check out www.abercare.sg for more details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants may send in your resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
